  "id": "RAW_7f9c84ec",
  "title": "刚刚，谷歌祭出迄今最前沿模型 Gemini 3 Flash！编程能力上反超 Gemini 3 Pro，且更快更便宜",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247651582&idx=1&sn=f6d9c0bda986ae2f26042d527035c66b",
  "date": "2025-12-17 18:15:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167902\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7eeae9a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavEdWrHPxX3WmibcPm1ib47oibPwhoL9pH1CiaI5QzvJkeemLllgRp46Plqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:13px 0px 0px;color:rgb(145, 145, 145);white-space:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:14px;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(145, 145, 145);text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 13px 0px 0px;padding-left: 14px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">作者 | 冬梅</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在大模型竞赛进入“效率与规模并重”的新阶段之际，谷歌正再次亮出王牌。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚刚，谷歌发布最新模型 Gemini 3 Flash，据介绍，它拥有前沿智能，专为速度而生，可以帮助每个人更快地学习、构建和规划任何事物。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">早在模型发布前，Google AI Studio 开发者平台 和 Gemini API 产品负责人 Logan Kilpatrick 就在 X 上发布了一条只有三个闪电符号的推文，当时就有大批网友猜测这意味着谷歌即将发布主打速度至上的 Flash 版本模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">果然，今晚谷歌 Gemini 3 Flash 模型如约而至。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167922\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4537037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e650099&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavicwnibclHc2Car3rPYzaEDfibAUkZBq2WXzmXzePu3PwHozJd7f5jLSrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251218080724_adcd7bde&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌发布其迄今最快 AI 模型&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去一年，从 Gemini 1.5 到 3.0，谷歌持续强化其在多模态、长上下文和推理能力上的技术纵深，同时也在不断压低模型调用成本，试图在企业级应用和开发者生态中建立更具性价比的护城河。在这一背景下，主打高性能与低延迟的 Flash 系列被视为 Gemini 体系中最贴近真实业务场景的一条产品线。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着外界对“更快、更便宜、更易部署”的模型呼声不断升高，谷歌今晚发布的 Gemini &nbsp;Flash 3，也被普遍认为是其在推理效率和规模化落地层面的一次关键落子。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌称，从今天起，Gemini 3 Flash 将面向全球数百万用户推出：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">适用于 Google AI Studio、Gemini CLI 和谷歌新的智能体开发平台 Google Antigravity 中的 Gemini API 开发者</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有用户均可通过 Gemini 应用和 AI 模式在搜索中使用。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">适用于 Vertex AI 和 Gemini Enterprise 的企业</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，这款模型性能到底怎样呢？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌在其官网介绍称，Gemini 3 Flash 速度和规模无需以牺牲智能为代价。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它在博士级别的推理和知识基准测试（例如 GPQA Diamond 90.4%) 和 Humanity's Last Exam (</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">33.7%，不使用工具</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">）中均展现出前沿性能，足以媲美规模更大的前沿模型，并且在多项基准测试中显著超越了目前最佳的 2.5 版本模型 Gemini 2.5 Pro。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 2.5 Flash 的得分为 11%，而最新发布的 GPT-5.2 的得分为 34.5%。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，它在 MMMU Pro 测试中也取得了令人瞩目的 81.2% 的成绩，与 Gemini 3 Pro 的性能相当。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167925\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.163\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3feac087&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavzGHgo1Ty1Yll7SIrrxsWm3LWqB7WAxF1xibc8RKs15BdPgpoIgibicS0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">除了前沿的推理能力和多模态处理能力外，Gemini 3 Flash 的设计目标是极高的效率，突破质量、成本和速度之间的帕累托极限。在最高思维水平下进行处理时，Gemini 3 Flash 能够灵活调整其思考时间。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251218080724_adcd7bde&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">性能优于 Gemini Pro 2.5，价格更低</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于更复杂的应用场景，它可能需要更长的思考时间，但根据典型流量的测试结果，它平均使用的 token 数量比 2.5 Pro 少 30%，从而以更高的性能更准确地完成日常任务。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167926\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cffc13dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavDnzRIcVaMJPfiaD1tw0aezIq477L4AicssOmek84f6d73EdyYKJN1xyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Gemini 3 Flash 在性能、成本和速度方面突破了帕累托极限。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Flash 的优势在于其极快的速度，它基于 Flash 系列产品打造而成。其性能超越 2.5 Pro，速度提升 3 倍（基于 Artificial Analysis 基准测试），而价格却低得多。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在定价方面，Gemini 3 Flash 相比前几代模型更具性价比。Gemini 3 Flash 的定价为每百万个输入 token 0.50 美元，每百万个输出 token 3 美元（音频输入价格仍为每百万个输入 token 1 美元）。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这比 Gemini Flash 2.5 的每百万个输入 token 0.30 美元和每百万个输出 token 2.50 美元略贵。但谷歌声称，新模型的性能优于 Gemini 2.5 Pro，速度更是其三倍。而且，在处理思维任务时，它平均比 2.5 Pro 少用 30% 的 token。这意味着，总体而言，在某些任务中，用户可能会节省 token 数量。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167924\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7bbf1fdc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavMtfagPL8bEB4h8j2paOJAwxhelT4FPYbsGb9ibcqFmCxo3qzH0CF7CA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在编程性能上，Gemini 3 Flash 拥有 Gemini 3 专业级的编码性能，同时延迟极低——能够在高频工作流程中快速推理和解决任务。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在用于评估编码代理能力的基准测试 SWE-bench Verified 中，Gemini 3 Flash 的得分高达 78%，不仅超越了 2.5 系列，甚至超越了 Gemini 3 Pro。它在代理编码、生产就绪系统和响应式交互式应用程序之间实现了理想的平衡。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167928\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e6b7bc9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavqUKHhJTuS68IodEvGwUlj6kxV7HAnO7vpnmbBOS5T4x556Rev47CUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Flash 在推理、工具使用和多模态功能方面的强大性能，非常适合希望进行更复杂的视频分析、数据提取和视觉问答的开发人员，这意味着它可以实现更智能的应用——例如游戏助手或 A/B 测试实验——这些应用既需要快速的答案，也需要深入的推理。</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Gemini 3 Flash 能够在手部追踪的“发射球益智游戏”中实现多模态推理，提供近乎实时的AI辅助。</span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Gemini 3 Flash 可以近乎实时地构建和 A/B 测试新的加载旋转器设计，从而简化从设计到编码的过程。</span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Gemini 3 Flash 使用多模态推理来分析图像并添加上下文 UI 叠加层，几乎可以实时地将静态图像转换为交互式体验。</span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">Gemini3 Flash 接受一条指令提示，并编码三种独特的设计变体。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，值得一提的是，Gemini 3 Flash 也开始作为搜索中 AI 模式的默认模型推出，全球用户均可使用。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于 Gemini 3 Pro 的推理能力，Gemini 3 Flash 的 AI 模式能够更有效地解析用户问题的细微差别。它会考虑用户查询的每一个方面，提供周全且易于理解的答案——从网络各处提取实时本地信息和实用链接。最终，它能有效地将研究与即时行动相结合：用户将获得一份条理清晰、条理分明的分析报告以及具体的建议——速度堪比搜索。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌方面表示，其将 Gemini Flash 的定位更偏向于“主力机型”，而非高端展示型模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini Models 高级总监兼产品负责人 Tulsee Doshi 在接受 TechCrunch 简报时指出，如果对比价格表中输入和输出的定价，可以明显看到 Flash 在成本上要低得多，这使其更适合承担大规模、批量化的任务处理需求，能够切实帮助企业降低使用门槛和整体成本。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">自 Gemini 3 发布以来，谷歌在其 API 上的处理规模迅速放大，目前每日处理的 token 数量已超过 1 万亿个。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，谷歌也正与 OpenAI 展开一场围绕新品发布节奏和模型性能的正面竞争。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有报道称，本月初，随着谷歌在消费者市场的份额上升，ChatGPT 的整体访问量出现下滑，OpenAI CEO Sam Altman 因此向内部团队发出了一份被称为“红色警报”的备忘录。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">随后，OpenAI 接连发布了 GPT-5.2 以及一款新的图像生成模型，并强调其企业级应用需求持续增长。OpenAI 还披露，自 2024 年 11 月以来，ChatGPT 的消息量已增长约 8 倍。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">尽管谷歌并未直接回应与 OpenAI 之间的竞争关系，但其认为，新模型的密集发布正在推动整个行业加速前进。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">“目前整个行业的状态是，各类模型都在快速演进，相互竞争、不断突破性能边界，”Doshi 表示，“同样令人印象深刻的是，各家公司都在非常积极地推出新模型。”</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">她同时提到，谷歌也在持续引入新的基准测试体系和模型评估方法，这一趋势本身也让团队对行业的发展感到振奋。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251218080724_adcd7bde&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">网友评价如何？</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">谷歌新模型发布后在全球引发了热烈讨论。在 X 和 Reddit 等平台上，大量开发者与技术爱好者对 Gemini 系列模型，特别是 Flash 版本，表达了多元观点。</span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在X上，有些用户使用过</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Gemini 3 Flash&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">后认为</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-align: center; margin: 0; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-line; line-height: 27px; padding: 23px 8px 0 8px; margin: 0; color: #4a4a4a;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Stagehand Agent 上</span><span leaf=\"\">它的准</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif; text-align: center; margin: 0; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400; font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-line; line-height: 27px; padding: 23px 8px 0 8px; margin: 0; color: #4a4a4a;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">确度几乎与 Gemini 3 Pro 不相上下，但价格更低，速度更快。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Browserbase 创始人 Paul Klein IV 在 X 上发文称，他们提前获得了 Gemini Flash 的访问权限，当真正用起它的那一刻，他们就惊呆了。他感慨道：</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Stagehand Agent 的准确度几乎与 Gemini 3 Pro 不相上下，但价格更低，速度更快。“</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167933\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8268518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dc6beded&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavGGhQNziaibj956uO1asU5PyxWYVrhiaxASticxrttRFst9QxdGEicyuFia1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Reddit 上，不禁有用户感叹，真是太疯狂了！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有用户表示从没见过能力这么强的轻量级模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167927\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39814814814814814\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1875d1f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siav6VpG7SuDkNcwKeHUZpyFQnia3frCJdVILZdGRCiaWmJzT2eblhAIVN4w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但也有用户指出，基准测试的成绩，并不能说明在真实场景中表现同样出色。</span></p>\n    <blockquote style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;border-left: none;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;margin: 0;margin-top: 27px;padding: 0 20px;color: #5baceb;\"><span leaf=\"\">“因为基准测试的成绩，并不能很好地对应真实使用场景。尤其是在实际应用中，使用场景往往非常多样，也远比那些单轮对话的基准测试样本复杂得多。坦率地说，看到 Flash 这种定位更轻量的模型在评分上“击败” Pro 版本，反而让我对这种为了刷基准分数的做法产生了怀疑。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;margin: 0;margin-top: 27px;padding: 0 20px;color: #5baceb;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其是最近几周，我一直在同时使用 Gemini 3 Pro 和 Opus 4.5，这两款模型本身都非常出色。但如果只看基准测试，Gemini 理应整体表现更强，可在实际使用中它却一次次让我失望；相反，Opus 4.5 却不断带来惊喜。”</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167930\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2972222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=407e1fe4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavNXPzvZW6AlGsFKUHkkicr5AicrqaEcrngM2Vprib4YVfTSI5ic9TaVI6iag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有用户认为，谷歌最近几次发布已经充分彰显了行业领头羊地位，OpenAI 似乎已经被拍在沙滩上了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100167929\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15555555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81e60c65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnE4Ov66H9Yw1TDtwBe8siavjDwWYKgTZlfrQVgFICr8kibCPb3tCwVVvFtcDOjsLMTf5REkzYeLgbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2025/12/17/google-launches-gemini-3-flash-makes-it-the-default-model-in-the-gemini-app/\" target=\"_blank\">https://techcrunch.com/2025/12/17/google-launches-gemini-3-flash-makes-it-the-default-model-in-the-gemini-app/</a></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://blog.google/products/search/google-ai-mode-update-gemini-3-flash/\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.google/products/search/google-ai-mode-update-gemini-3-flash/</a></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3-flash/\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3-flash/</a></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌最新发布了 Gemini 3 Flash 模型，其在编程能力上反超 Gemini 3 Pro，且以更快的速度和更低的成本为开发者和企业提供前沿智能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌最新发布了 Gemini 3 Flash 模型，其在编程能力上反超 Gemini 3 Pro，且以更快的速度和更低的成本为开发者和企业提供前沿智能。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了谷歌最新发布的 Gemini 3 Flash 模型，该模型专为速度和效率而生，旨在降低大规模 AI 应用的门槛。它在多项前沿基准测试中展现出与大型模型媲美的性能，尤其在编程能力（SWE-bench Verified 得分 78%）上表现突出，甚至超越了 Gemini 3 Pro。Gemini 3 Flash 在定价上更具竞争力，每百万个输入/输出 Token 价格分别为 0.50 美元和 3 美元，并且平均使用的 Token 数量比 2.5 Pro 少 30%。该模型将广泛应用于 Google AI Studio、Gemini CLI、Google Antigravity 开发者平台、Gemini 应用、AI 模式搜索以及 Vertex AI 企业级服务。文章还探讨了当前大模型市场的激烈竞争，并通过用户反馈展示了对 Gemini 3 Flash 的积极评价与部分关于基准测试与实际应用差异的质疑。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Flash 在效率、速度和成本上实现突破，旨在满足大规模业务场景需求。",
      "explanation": "模型专为速度和规模化落地设计，以更低的成本提供更快的推理速度，突破了传统模型在质量、成本和速度间的帕累托极限，使其成为企业和开发者的“主力机型”。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Flash 的编程性能超越 Gemini 3 Pro，更适合开发高频交互应用。",
      "explanation": "在 SWE-bench Verified 基准测试中，Gemini 3 Flash 得分高达 78%，高于 Gemini 3 Pro，表明其在代理编码、生产系统和响应式应用开发中具备强大实力，能在低延迟下快速推理并解决任务。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型支持多模态推理，可实现复杂的视频分析、数据提取和视觉问答。",
      "explanation": "Gemini 3 Flash 的强大多模态功能使其能够应用于游戏助手、A/B 测试、实时交互式 UI 叠加等智能应用，提供快速且深入的推理，将静态图像转换为交互式体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Flash 成为 Google AI 模式搜索的默认模型，显著提升用户体验。",
      "explanation": "该模型能更有效地解析用户查询意图，提供周全且易于理解的答案，结合实时本地信息和实用链接，有效地将信息研究与即时行动相结合，速度堪比传统搜索。"
    },
    {
      "point": "市场对 Gemini 3 Flash 评价积极，但基准测试与实际应用表现仍存争议。",
      "explanation": "部分用户赞扬其接近 Pro 模型的准确度和更快的速度，但也有用户指出基准测试结果不完全等同于复杂多样的实际应用场景表现，需更全面的评估。"
    }
